metadata.name: Don Chulo Christopher
metadata.description:
𝕳𝕺𝕸𝕬𝕲𝕰 (Homage) is a collection of exclusive one of ones generated from 𝕿𝖍𝖊 𝕻𝖆𝖓𝖙𝖍𝖊𝖗'𝖘 𝕳𝖊𝖆𝖉 AI Protocol.

𝕿𝖍𝖊 𝕻𝖆𝖓𝖙𝖍𝖊𝖗'𝖘 𝕳𝖊𝖆𝖉 offers a unique take on the amalgamation of art, culture, and tech. Crafting one of a kind pieces of art of expression on a very high level.

"ɴᴏ ʜᴜᴍᴀɴꜱ ᴡᴇʀᴇ ʜᴀʀᴍᴇᴅ ᴍᴀᴋɪɴɢ ᴛʜɪꜱ ᴀʀᴛ"

Ownership will grant the holder the rights of the image, and please share credit with the project for awareness.

The collection is a fun way to experiment with art with the key figures that have been a big part of my growth in the space. This is my way of having fun with it in a artistic manner.

I wanted to immortalize them with wonderful art to remind them of the good times.

Community, and fun is a big part of what we are.

I really appreciate you all dearly.

I love you all, and thank you for being cool.
